    "causal_summary": "Phase 011 revives the long-deferred T1 acceptance-criteria coverage gate. The 2026-06-02 peck-README pass produced teachings T1-T4 and deferred T1; the peck-source deep-mining pass (research 006, 13 discovery iterations plus 5 cross-model verify iterations) re-evaluated T1 and found it now adoptable as a staged, reuse-heavy sibling packet. Post-026 the validation, checklist, and deep-review substrate already exists, so T1 becomes an AC-traceability table plus an `AC_COVERAGE` rule (floor 0.9, WARNING graduating to ERROR) plus a deep-review verdict binding with per-level AND lifecycle opt-in, reusing existing AC columns, the `EVIDENCE_CITED` infrastructure, and the fresh-context reviewer primitive.",
